    <item>
      <title>Render a record vertically</title>
      <link>https://benmatselby.dev/tidbits/mysql/render-record-vertically/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://benmatselby.dev/tidbits/mysql/render-record-vertically/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Sometimes you want to see a record in MySQL rendered vertically, especially if it has many columns. You can do this using the &lt;code&gt;\G&lt;/code&gt; command at the end of your query.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sql&#34; data-lang=&#34;sql&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;mysql&amp;gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;select&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;User&lt;/span&gt;,&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;Host&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;from&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;user&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a61717;background-color:#e3d2d2&#34;&gt;\&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;G&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;***************************&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#3677a9&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;row&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;***************************&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;User&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;root&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;Host&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;%&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;***************************&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#3677a9&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;row&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;***************************&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;User&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;mysql.infoschema&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;Host&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;localhost&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
